'''印度海軍'''（[[印地语|印地语]]：भारतीय नौसेना，拉丁转写：Bhartiya Nāu Senā）擁有60000余人，其中有5000余名[[海軍航空兵|海軍航空兵]]和2000余名[[海軍陸戰隊|海軍陸戰隊]]。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/navy-intro.htm |title=Global Security article on the Indian Navy |accessdate=2009-12-26 |archive-date=2011-05-11 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20110511142418/http://www.globalsecurity.org/military/world/india/navy-intro.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref>{{Cite web |url=http://pib.nic.in/release/release.asp?relid=51144&kwd= |title=Fast Interceptor boats for Sagar Prahari Bal |access-date=2009-12-26 |archive-date=2016-03-03 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303235659/http://pib.nic.in/release/release.asp?relid=51144&kwd= |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.thomaspmbarnett.com/published/12steps.htm |title=India's 12 Steps to a World-Class Navy |accessdate=2009-12-26 |archive-date=2007-10-14 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20071014183557/http://thomaspmbarnett.com/published/12steps.htm |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.hinduonnet.com/fline/fl2103/stories/20040213003603500.htm |title=The Gorshkov deal |accessdate=2009-12-26 |archive-date=2009-01-10 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20090110125143/http://www.hinduonnet.com/fline/fl2103/stories/20040213003603500.htm |dead-url=no }}</ref>近年來，印度廣泛進行海軍現代化和發展，除了積極向外國購買多艘船艦外，也開發出國產[[核潛艇|核潛艇]]及[[航空母舰|航空母舰]]，目前擁有超過200余艘正在服役的軍艦，旗舰为[[維蘭瑪迪雅號航空母艦|維蘭瑪迪雅號航空母艦]]，成為[[藍水海軍|藍水海軍]]，力圖與世界海軍強國在[[印度洋|印度洋]]的勢力及鄰國[[巴基斯坦|巴基斯坦]]相抗衡，其主要目標是保護國家海洋邊界、加強國際關係、人道主義救援。<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.jmss.org/2008/winter/articles/scott.pdf |title=India's drive for a 'Blue water' Navy by Dr. David Scott, International Relations, Brunel University |accessdate=2009-12-26 |archive-date=2008-05-28 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20080528002213/http://www.jmss.org/2008/winter/articles/scott.pdf |dead-url=yes }}</ref><ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.indian-military.org/indian-military-reports/india